    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">These small glass vials with screw cap come case packed with 144 pieces in each vial set. They are ideal for storing liquids with their water tight screw on plastic cap or storing small items like beads, glitter, dust and other essential craft and hobby items. They will perform well in all laboratory conditions and are manufactured to the high quality standards to ensure they will work as expected each time without fail. These small dram vials are made from Borosilicate glass, which is a type of glass that will not crack under extreme temperature changes like regular glass. Its durability has made it the glass of choice for laboratories, scientists, prospectors and collectors alike</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">144pk Glass Vial Collection Set Craft and Hobby Storage</h2>\n  <p>These small glass vials with screw cap come case packed with 144 pieces in each vial set. They are ideal for storing liquids with their water tight screw on plastic cap or storing small items like beads, glitter, dust and other essential craft and hobby items. They will perform well in all laboratory conditions and are manufactured to the high quality standards to ensure they will work as expected each time without fail.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Borosilicate small glass vials with screw on cap. Water tight liquid seal. Will not crack or break under extreme temperature changes</li>\n    <li>Clear transparent vial body with black cap</li>\n    <li>144 individual small dram glass vials with screw cap come case packed in each vial set</li>\n    <li>Widely used in laboratory environments. Excellent resistance to corrosion and low moisture absorption. Making these lab sample vials able to be used with an autoclave</li>\n    <li>Perfect for storing small items like gold flakes, glitter, essential oils, perfume, gems, beads, and more</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/camping_outdoors/goldProducts/144pcSmallGlassVials1.jpg\" alt=\"These small glass vials with screw cap come case packed with 144 pieces in each vial set\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 144SV-1-137</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058486264</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>These small dram vials are made from Borosilicate glass, which is a type of glass that will not crack under extreme temperature changes like regular glass. Its durability has made it the glass of choice for laboratories, scientists, prospectors and collectors alike.</p>\n  <p>In addition to the glass body tube, the caps them selves which screw on are made from a thermoset plastic material known for its physical and molding properties. These caps show strength and durability with heat-resistant and insulating properties that are widely used in laboratory environments. Excellent resistance to corrosion and low moisture absorption. Making these lab sample vials able to be used with an autoclave.</p>\n  <p>These are the vials you want whether it is working in a laboratory or at home with your hobby and crafts, essential oils, beading or glitter. They perform the job without fail.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "These small glass vials with screw cap come case packed with 144 pieces in each vial set. They are ideal for storing liquids with their water tight screw on plastic cap or storing small items like beads, glitter, dust and other essential craft and hobby items. They will perform well in all laboratory conditions and are manufactured to the high quality standards to ensure they will work as expected each time without fail. These small dram vials are made from Borosilicate glass, which is a type of glass that will not crack under extreme temperature changes like regular glass. Its durability has made it the glass of choice for laboratories, scientists, prospectors and collectors alike.",
